      "Heat a skillet on medium heat. Add a teaspoon of oil, spread this all over the skillet using a clean absorbent kitchen towel, in such a way as to coat the surface well, but not visible.",
      "Place the shaped black-eyed bean kebabs on the skillet. Cook the kebabs on medium heat.",
      "After about 2-3 minutes or after the under-side turns brown, flip carefully using a flat spatula.",
